      Optional dependency hook: loaded only when Spring / Spring-MVC plugins are
      installed. The Spring-aware code paths in CrossLanguageResolver detect
      annotations through PSI on the classpath (`PsiAnnotation`), which works
      whether or not the Spring plugin is loaded — so this file is intentionally
      empty. It exists so IntelliJ wires the optional <depends> entries cleanly.
    -->
